high_descs: Go straight and to the right, towards the gray sofa.
Pick up the red pen from the couch.
Turn back around past the couch, then turn right into the bedroom and approach the large shelf in the corner of the room.
Place the red pen on the high shelf of the desk.
Exit the room the way you came in, then turn right into the kitchen area, towards the sink.
Take the red pen from the sink area.
Return to the large shelf you placed the first pen on.
Place the pen next to the first one on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place two red pens on a desk shelf in a bedroom.

high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the sofa on your right.
Pick up pen from the sofa.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the shelf.
Place pen on the shelf.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near sink.
Pick up pen from the sofa.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the shelf.
Place pen on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Collecting pen from different places and arranging them on a shelf.

high_descs: Take left and move forward then turn right move to the sofa to your right.
Take the pen from the sofa.
Turn right and move toward the shelf, then take a right, head toward the locker, then hang to the right.
Put the pen into the shelf.
Turn around and move forward then turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the pen from the sink.
Turn around and move toward the shelf, take left, head toward the locker then hang to right.
Place the pen into the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Collect the pen and place it on the shelf.
